Package: figma
Type: Package
Title: R client to the Figma API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pedro Duarte Faria
Maintainer: Pedro Duarte Faria <pedropark99@gmail.com>
Description: An easy-to-use client/wrapper for the Figma API.
  It allows you to bring all data from a Figma file to your R session. This includes the data of all objects that you have drawn in this file, and their respective canvas/page metadata.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
