    httr (>= 1.4.1),
    purrr (>= 0.3.3),
    dplyr (>= 1.0.0),
    rlang (>= 1.0.0),
    tibble (>= 3.0.5)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    usethis,
    emoji
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
